Gets details about a bill including outstanding balance, due date, status, and payment history.

### HTTP Request

`POST <%= config.host %>/bill/detail`

### Post Parameters

Param | Description
----- | -----------
`userId` | Unbill user ID.
`companyId` | Unbill company ID.

### 200 Response Body

Attribute | Description
--------- | -----------
`bill` | Bill data.
`bill.balance` | Current balance.
`bill.dueDate` | Current Current due date.
`bill.status` | Current Status `paid, pending, upcoming, overdue, syncing`.
`company` | Bill company data.
`company.name` | Name of the company.
`company.logo` | URL of the company logo.
`company.paysRent` | Whether this company accepts rent payments (if true, the logo looks best as a background image)
`payments` | List of past bill payments
`payments.amount` | Amount paid
`payments.paidOn` | Date of payment